00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,960
The Prince of Tennis
~ Match! Tennis Juniors! ~

21
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,280
[Jiuxin] Who is that person?

22
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,960
[player 1] Seems like it's Lu Xia
from Yu Qing.

23
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:54,720
I wanted to teach the players
in Ying Cai a lesson myself.

24
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:57,840
[scoffs]
Seems like somebody is doing that already.

25
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,640
[He Xinglong] What happened? Don't cry.

26
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,600
Let's meet tonight.

27
00:02:01,960 --> 00:02:03,600
I have a huge secret to tell you.

28
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:05,040
-Be quick.
-[Tang Jiale grunts]

29
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,040
How is that?

30
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:08,000
[Qiao Chen] Xinglong.

31
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:11,000
I heard he has a date tonight.

32
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:12,480
Go and find him.

33
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:16,200
[Yan Zhiming] No wonder Xinglong
has been absentminded recently.

34
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:19,360
[sighs]

35
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,680
-He Xinglong!
-[Qiao Chen] Xinglong!

36
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,440
-He Xinglong!
-Xinglong!

37
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,800
Lu Xia, did you see He Xinglong?

38
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:28,720
He left.

39
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,720
[clicks tongue]
Why didn't you ask him to stay?

40
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:34,320
We could find out
who he is going to date tonight.

41
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:36,040
-He has a date with me.
-Huh?

42
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,600
No way! Why do you have a date?

43
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,680
Lately, we practice tennis together
in the evening.

44
00:02:41,760 --> 00:02:42,680
[Qiao Chen] Oh...

45
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,440
He "dated" Lu Xia.

46
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:46,760
[sighs]

47
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:50,240
It seems like it isn't about love.

48
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,960
[sighs]

49
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,440
[He Xinglong and Mr. He grunts]

50
00:02:57,520 --> 00:03:00,280
Dad, the geese that I picked this morning
have been sent here,

51
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,360
I think they are good.

52
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,960
Like you said,
their feet should have calluses,

53
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:06,360
their feathers are smooth,
and their voices are deep,

54
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:08,520
-they're definitely free-range geese.
-Good boy.

55
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,400
-You know a lot better about geese.
-[chuckles]

56
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,680
In the future,
our restaurant will count on you.

57
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,280
[chuckles]

58
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:18,160
Oh, a few days ago,
the coach who taught you Tae Kwon Do

59
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:20,040
still asked about you
when he came for a meal.

60
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,760
[Mr. He] He asked why you
quit Tae Kwon Do.

61
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:24,560
Oh. I wanted to learn many things
when I was young.

62
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,480
But since I started to learn tennis,

63
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,960
I began to know what I really like.

64
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:31,480
It is good. You have to try everything

65
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:33,200
before you know
what you really want to do.

66
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,160
Mm-hm.

67
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,760
Are you going to have a match?

68
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,040
-Yes.
-You can go and practice.

69
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,920
I will practice after I'm finished here.

70
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,360
[chuckles]
Okay.

71
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,280
[soft chuckle]

72
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,320
[ball thumps]

73
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:51,360
[cell phone ringing]

74
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:56,400
-Hello.
-[He Xinglong] Hello, Lu Xia.

75
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,680
Are you still at the court?

76
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:01,320
-When will you come?
-[He Xinglong] I am really sorry,

77
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,720
I have some urgent business to do.

78
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,720
-I'm sorry.
-It doesn't matter.

79
00:04:06,200 --> 00:04:08,200
[somber music]

80
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:11,600
[sighs]

81
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,400
[thumps]

82
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:16,240
[sighs deeply]

83
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,600
[sobbing]

84
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:38,080
[ominous music]

85
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:40,440
[sobbing]

86
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,960
[foreboding music]

87
00:04:54,520 --> 00:04:56,560
[Min sobbing]

88
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:03,560
[Yu Qing players panting]

89
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:09,840
YU QING HIGH SCHOOL TENNIS CLUB
QUALIFYING

90
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,640
I am exhausted.

91
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,560
[whimpers]

92
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,840
[all panting]

93
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:31,040
Why has our training plan become torturous

94
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:35,080
after Yan observed Ying Cai's training?

95
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:38,080
Maybe he suffered a blow
when observing them.

96
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:41,920
You have to cheer up,
the team will count on you in the future.

97
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,840
Huh? Okay.

98
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:47,200
[all panting]

99
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:52,040
[He Xinglong grunting]

100
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,360
[Dayong] Xinglong, what happened to you?

101
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,080
Why haven't you talked to us all day?

102
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:00,560
You can tell me if you feel uncomfortable.

103
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,160
Don't force yourself.

104
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:05,760
[soft chuckle]
I am okay. Don't worry.

105
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,600
The 86th lap.

106
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,720
[Yan Zhiming] Continue.

107
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:14,840
[all groaning, panting]

108
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,320
[He Xinglong] Lu Xia...

109
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:23,040
I am sorry for not going to the court
to practice with you

110
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,640
and for keeping you waiting.

111
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:27,360
Then will you have time to practice
with me in the future?

112
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,800
[chuckles]
Of course.

113
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:31,440
As long as I help my father
with the things in the restaurant,

114
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:34,880
and you don't think it is too late,
I will always play with you.

115
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,880
Okay.
[laughs]

116
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:43,160
Burning! Yeah!

117
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,520
You missed the tenth ball.

118
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,320
You should buy me drinks for a week.

119
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:55,160
Don't refuse. We had a deal.

120
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:57,280
You still have one ball to go.

121
00:06:58,160 --> 00:07:02,160
That's right, man.
If you miss the ball, we'll be tied.

122
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:04,920
I designed the fun training
especially for you.

123
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,440
Even if it is a tie,
you should still buy me a drink.

124
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,720
It sounds reasonable.

125
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,320
-I... Uh...
-In order to make you buy me drinks,

126
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,800
I will show you some real strength.

127
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,760
[tense music]

128
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,560
Do you have a player here named Lu Xia?

129
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,840
Tell him to come here.

130
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,560
Are you looking for Lu Xia?

131
00:07:46,640 --> 00:07:48,760
[Huang Jing sighs]
Dude.

132
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,680
I don't care who you are looking for.

133
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,520
You can't throw trash on our court.

134
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:55,720
[gasps]

135
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:03,520
We just cleaned it up.

136
00:08:05,880 --> 00:08:09,240
[Xiuwen whimpering]

137
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:19,320
[yelling]

138
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,720
-[Huang Jing and Mu gasp]
-[Xiuwen groans]

139
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:27,080
Whatever I do doesn't concern you.

140
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:29,680
[Xiuwen panting]

141
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,960
Is this a boring game that Yu Qing plays?

142
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,840
You can try it if you want.

143
00:08:41,880 --> 00:08:42,720
[scoffs]

144
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,919
Uh?

145
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,480
[tense music]

146
00:08:58,720 --> 00:08:59,640
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

147
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,800
[Mu groaning]

148
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,960
You...

149
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:08,000
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

150
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,040
-[ball thumps]
-[groans]

151
00:09:09,880 --> 00:09:12,800
[panting]

152
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:26,600
Why does the cleaning
take Mu and the seniors so long?

153
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,440
[sighs]

154
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,400
[Xiuwen sighs]

155
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,880
[whimpers]

156
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,360
[groans]

157
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,840
[gasps]

158
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,840
This is the ability of the players
of Yu Qing High School.

159
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:54,000
[Jiuxin] You can't even take the serve.

160
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,280
[Lu Xia] The racket is used
for playing tennis,

161
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,400
not for pointing at people.

162
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,960
[thunder rumbling]

163
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,600
[Ying panting]

164
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:12,520
[sighs]

165
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,400
[breathing heavily]

166
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,120
Are you Lu Xia?

167
00:10:16,640 --> 00:10:19,160
Do you want to talk to me?
I don't know you.

168
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:25,640
Do you play such a boring game every day?

169
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:27,040
What do you want?

170
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:29,560
[Ying panting]

171
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:32,480
Lu Xia, I have informed the security.

172
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,360
I hope you can get to the next round.

173
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,080
[Jiuxin]
So we can meet in the competition.

174
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,520
I will teach you a lesson there.

175
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,920
[tense music]

176
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,080
[thwacks]

177
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,320
[Xiuwen whimpering]

178
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:56,600
[Ying gasps]

179
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:59,800
[calm music]

180
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,200
[gasps]

181
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:17,880
-[breathing heavily]
-Don't worry, I am okay.

182
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:23,960
Lu Xia.

183
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:37,640
Go and tell He Xinglong
to mind his own business.

184
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,240
[calm music]

185
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,280
Lu Xia,

186
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,600
bear with it for a moment.

187
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:11,560
-It will be quick.
-Mm-hm.

188
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,520
[sucks teeth]

189
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,200
Sorry, I didn't mean to hurt you.

190
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,440
[sighs]

191
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:27,040
[sucks teeth]

192
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:29,880
[blows air]

193
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,480
Don't tell them.

194
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,600
Huh?

195
00:12:37,560 --> 00:12:38,720
Tell them what?

196
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:39,760
[inhales sharply]

197
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:41,760
Ah!

198
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,800
Why can't I tell them?

199
00:12:45,560 --> 00:12:46,440
It's just...

200
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:49,040
I don't want to tell them.

201
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,960
[laughs]

202
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:52,880
I know.

203
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,320
-Keep it a secret.
-Don't laugh.

204
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:56,920
[Ying laughs]

205
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:01,720
You saved me just now.

206
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:08,320
I think, next time,
you should deal with it another way.

207
00:13:09,280 --> 00:13:12,360
You don't have to be in conflict
with such people.

208
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:17,240
[Lu Xia sighs deeply]

209
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:20,120
Okay.

210
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:24,880
It is just a scratch.

211
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,320
[Qiao Chen] Senior,

212
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:35,080
Huang Jing told me Lu Xia was hurt
by someone.

213
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:36,320
[all] Huh?

214
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,000
No way.

215
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:39,440
Where did he get hurt?

216
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:41,120
Luckily, it's just a scratch.

217
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:43,280
But I heard it was a person
from No. 3 High School.

218
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:45,520
[ominous music]

219
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:47,280
If we defeat Ying Cai,

220
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:50,240
then we may compete against
No. 3 High School in the municipal final.

221
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,160
Mm-hm.

222
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:53,440
It is Shen Qianshi's high school.

223
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:58,560
I think we should tell the coach.

224
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:01,920
Uh...

225
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:05,240
Lu Xia, what happened to your face?

226
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,800
I slipped.

227
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:09,800
How can you be hurt like this
if you just slipped?

228
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:13,280
[Dayong] Shall we complain to the
National League Organizing Committee?

229
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:15,480
I just slipped and fell.

230
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:18,280
Xiuwen has told me the whole thing.
Don't pretend anymore.

231
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:21,160
[Dayong sighs]
Lu Xia, who was it?

232
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,480
[Dayong] Does the coach know?

233
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:30,480
Ah. See, this boy seems determined
to solve the matter himself.

234
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:33,800
Uh, how about this? I will pay.

235
00:14:33,880 --> 00:14:35,680
[Tang Jiale]
Let's treat Lu Xia to a good meal.

236
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:37,720
What do you think?
Chi, Xinglong, will you join us?

237
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:39,040
I'm the first to agree.

238
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:40,880
Next time. I have homework to do.

239
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:43,760
Xinglong, you can go with them.

240
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:46,360
Thank you, but I already have
an arrangement tonight.

241
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:48,800
Uh, never mind, we can go together.

242
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,960
Let's go.

243
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:53,320
[ominous music]

244
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:01,520
Lu Xia, how about it? Are you happy now?

245
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:02,480
Yes.

246
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:07,360
[sighs]

247
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:09,600
Senior, don't mind the cost.

248
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:12,440
Lu Xia has been bullied,
just think of this as comforting him.

249
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:15,520
[Lu Xia]
I said it was just because I slipped.

250
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,840
[gasps]
Wait a minute.

251
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:24,040
[Qiao Chen] Is that Xinglong?

252
00:15:35,520 --> 00:15:38,000
It seems that the information
I have on Xinglong can be revised.

253
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,160
[Tang Jiale gasps]

254
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:43,760
[comical music]

255
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:47,640
[Qiao Chen sighs]

256
00:15:51,680 --> 00:15:53,800
Xinglong looks different.

257
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:55,160
Mm-hm.

258
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:02,920
[foreboding music]

259
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:05,560
[Tang Jiale] Huh?

260
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:07,520
Who is that?

261
00:16:07,880 --> 00:16:09,360
What are they doing here?

262
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,160
What's their relationship?

263
00:16:16,760 --> 00:16:20,080
Yan, what are you writing?

264
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:24,360
The tiny things in life can also influence
the results of a tennis match.

265
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:27,000
[Tang Jiale sighs]

266
