I was already leading, 4-3.
I was about to win.

522
00:31:30,600 --> 00:31:33,280
Things like this shouldn't happen again.

523
00:31:33,360 --> 00:31:35,560
It is just training, not a competition.

524
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:39,000
[Coach Qi] Why did you continue to play
when it was raining hard?

525
00:31:39,080 --> 00:31:41,600
If you get hurt, who will be the one
to take responsibility?

526
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:44,720
Coach, please take it easy.

527
00:31:45,480 --> 00:31:46,440
[sighs]

528
00:31:46,520 --> 00:31:47,600
I agree.

529
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:49,760
This was my plan.

530
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:52,320
I will let you have competitions
with one another after training

531
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:55,960
because Ying Cai trains a lot more
than we do.

532
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,240
We can't ignore them.

533
00:31:57,320 --> 00:32:00,640
But there shouldn't be accidents
even if we add on the amount of training.

534
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,560
[sighs]

535
00:32:01,640 --> 00:32:04,840
We have to make sure
we can complete in our best condition.

536
00:32:05,480 --> 00:32:07,760
Huh? Speaking of which,

537
00:32:07,840 --> 00:32:10,320
how much more is the amount
of training in Ying Cai?

538
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:12,400
It is much more than you can imagine.

539
00:32:13,840 --> 00:32:15,880
[sighs]
Don't worry,

540
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:18,720
with my vertical smash and our Captain,

541
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,960
defeating Ying Cai
will be a piece of cake.

542
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:27,200
Anyway, Zhuo Zhi and Lu Xia,
you have finished your training.

543
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:30,640
Others, please continue as planned.

544
00:32:31,520 --> 00:32:34,200
-For the next pair, Qiao Chen...
-Good.

545
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:36,560
I can't let Lu Xia steal the spotlight.

546
00:32:37,880 --> 00:32:39,400
Who dares to suffer defeat at my hand?

547
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:43,840
Me.

548
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:46,520
[playful music]

549
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:51,720
Damn!

550
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:53,600
It is the captain.

551
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:55,520
How lucky.

552
00:33:01,920 --> 00:33:03,360
[Qiao Chen] It is a rare opportunity.

553
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:07,960
I will try my best and let the captain see
how much progress I have made.

554
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:12,360
-[thwacking]
-[both grunting]

555
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:20,400
[grunts]

556
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,560
[ball thumping]

557
00:33:25,320 --> 00:33:27,120
[pants]

558
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:36,080
-[thwacking]
-[ball thumping]

559
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:58,240
[panting]

560
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:14,880
You are really marvelous, Captain.

561
00:34:16,040 --> 00:34:17,040
I lost, anyway.

562
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:21,800
Qiao Chen, why do you think
you are the loser?

563
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:23,480
That is obvious.

564
00:34:24,719 --> 00:34:26,000
You are so strong.

565
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,280
How can I defeat you?

566
00:34:29,159 --> 00:34:31,159
You had a chance to defeat me.

567
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:33,360
Your arm.

568
00:34:35,560 --> 00:34:38,080
The wound on your feet
seems to have fully recovered.

569
00:34:38,639 --> 00:34:40,760
But if you can't leave the memory
of being hurt behind,

570
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:43,760
you won't be able to exercise
your real power.

571
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:48,280
[Siyang] Qiao Chen, believe in yourself.

572
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:57,960
[keys jangling]

573
00:34:59,679 --> 00:35:00,560
[snickers]

574
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,080
[sighs]

575
00:35:11,240 --> 00:35:13,600
Were you in the same condition
when you competed with Lu Xia?

576
00:35:15,120 --> 00:35:17,440
-You know that.
-I guessed right.

577
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:22,880
Having a match with him is fun.

578
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:26,280
It is rare for you to compete seriously.

579
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:29,560
If it hadn't rained, maybe the result
would have been different.

580
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:32,760
[snickers]
Let's compete together...

581
00:35:33,880 --> 00:35:35,520
when your arm recovers.

582
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:39,120
Yan keeps saying
that your data is extremely vague.

583
00:35:41,040 --> 00:35:43,640
Why not try your best for once?

584
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:46,560
Because I enjoy seeing
my opponents try their best.

585
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,600
What about you?

586
00:35:52,240 --> 00:35:54,560
[sighs deeply]

587
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:58,040
What I am thinking about now
is leading Yu Qing

588
00:35:58,440 --> 00:36:00,240
to go further in the national competition.

589
00:36:03,120 --> 00:36:04,280
Then we will see.

590
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:07,080
Bye.

591
00:36:08,120 --> 00:36:11,280
[Siyang sighs deeply]

592
00:36:15,920 --> 00:36:16,960
[exhales sharply]

593
00:36:20,680 --> 00:36:23,240
What a pity, the rain came at a bad time.

594
00:36:23,640 --> 00:36:24,520
Mm-hm.

595
00:36:26,200 --> 00:36:30,200
Senior, you can't defeat the captain
even with your Vertical Smash, right?

596
00:36:30,840 --> 00:36:32,040
Shut up!

597
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:40,560
Let's compete now.

598
00:36:44,160 --> 00:36:45,680
But won't it hurt your feelings...

599
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:48,040
if you lose twice in a day?

600
00:36:49,440 --> 00:36:50,920
[breathes heavily]

601
00:36:51,680 --> 00:36:53,680
[playful music]

602
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:01,600
Yu Qing is interesting.

603
00:37:02,400 --> 00:37:03,360
Huh?

604
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:06,920
