in one team.

605
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:08,280
[scoffs]

606
00:37:09,440 --> 00:37:10,680
Shouldn't it be three?

607
00:37:18,080 --> 00:37:20,360
[Yu] Let me drink some protein powder
to gain some strength.

608
00:37:25,680 --> 00:37:27,640
-[cell phone ringing]
-[gasps]

609
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:35,400
-Hello, Zhi. What's the matter?
-[Zhuo Zhi] Nothing,

610
00:37:36,080 --> 00:37:38,320
I just wanted to call you.
What are you doing?

611
00:37:38,520 --> 00:37:41,080
Training. If you are okay with it,
I will hang up.

612
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:44,160
[Zhuo Zhi] I had a competition
with Lu Xia today.

613
00:37:44,640 --> 00:37:45,480
[gasps]
Did you win?

614
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:50,440
No, I mean, did Lu Xia win?

615
00:37:50,640 --> 00:37:51,680
[Zhuo Zhi] Yu,

616
00:37:52,000 --> 00:37:54,400
Yu Qing is really strong.

617
00:37:55,520 --> 00:37:57,200
Give me the phone, I'll talk to him.

618
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:03,000
Are you gathering information
on your opponents?

619
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:05,320
-I won't...
-[dial tone beeping]

620
00:38:07,680 --> 00:38:09,800
-What's wrong?
-Let's go.

621
00:38:09,880 --> 00:38:11,600
I will watch you train.

622
00:38:11,680 --> 00:38:14,840
But I have just finished my training.

623
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:18,680
Do you think you can defeat your brother
with such little training?

624
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:21,360
[Yue] Let's go.

625
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,800
I will plan your training for you.

626
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:34,480
[school bell tolling]

627
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:38,120
Only those who pass all the exams
can continue playing in the competition?

628
00:38:39,120 --> 00:38:41,320
Plus, the Municipal Tennis Final
is about to take place.

629
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:43,320
Such a requirement can only

630
00:38:43,440 --> 00:38:45,800
make it more difficult for us
to win the championship.

631
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:48,840
It is a basic requirement

632
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:52,560
for a senior high student
to pass the monthly exams.

633
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:57,440
Yan, please reduce the training time
as much as you can for this week.

634
00:38:58,040 --> 00:38:59,840
[Siyang] This will give the team members

635
00:39:00,520 --> 00:39:02,840
who failed the exams enough time to study.

636
00:39:02,920 --> 00:39:06,880
That means, from now on,
if I find any of you

637
00:39:07,440 --> 00:39:09,720
doing something
apart from study and training...

638
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:11,960
-I love studying.
-Studying makes me happy.

639
00:39:13,680 --> 00:39:14,720
[sighs]

640
00:39:15,120 --> 00:39:17,240
[background chatter]

641
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:19,840
LIBRARY

642
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:20,760
YU QING

643
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:23,000
If there are three short choices
and one long choice...

644
00:39:23,880 --> 00:39:25,000
We should choose the longest.

645
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:32,160
If there are three long choices
and one short choice...

646
00:39:33,040 --> 00:39:33,880
Choose the shortest.

647
00:39:35,560 --> 00:39:37,760
If the lengths of the choices
are irregular...

648
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:39,240
Choose...

649
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:40,640
Choose the letter C.

650
00:39:42,160 --> 00:39:43,120
How do you know that?

651
00:39:44,080 --> 00:39:46,560
No matter how long or short,
C is the best.

652
00:39:47,560 --> 00:39:48,640
Oh!

653
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:50,760
Brilliant.

654
00:39:51,800 --> 00:39:52,640
C.

655
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:55,880
Frankly speaking,
the library is comfortable,

656
00:39:56,320 --> 00:39:58,400
quiet, and has an air-conditioner.

657
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:01,560
As long as Yan is not here,
I can stay here for a whole day.

658
00:40:02,920 --> 00:40:04,160
Qiao Chen, Baiyang.

659
00:40:10,160 --> 00:40:13,360
According to your grades,
the number of exercises you should do...

660
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:16,680
needs to double.

661
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:17,960
[Qiao Chen] I am finished.

662
00:40:18,040 --> 00:40:20,080
I probably won't be able to play
in the competition.

663
00:40:25,680 --> 00:40:28,880
[Tang Jiale sighs]
What can I do? I am so stressed.

664
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:31,400
Should we start to study now?

665
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:34,800
I think I tried hard
in the last monthly test.

666
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:36,320
I only failed two exams.

667
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:37,640
[scoffs]

668
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:40,280
We will win even if you are not playing.

669
00:40:41,200 --> 00:40:44,080
-Then we can compete to see.
-All right, let's have a match.

670
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:46,080
Forget it. Don't do that.

671
00:40:46,160 --> 00:40:48,680
If we fail the exam again,
no one can play in the competition.

672
00:40:48,760 --> 00:40:51,480
[Tang Jiale] We have to review and study
instead of talking needlessly.

673
00:40:51,560 --> 00:40:52,400
That is a good idea.

674
00:40:52,480 --> 00:40:54,080
We can supervise each other.

675
00:40:54,160 --> 00:40:56,680
-Anyway, it is the weekend tomorrow.
